# Build-context filter for the root-context Docker builds (ai-worker,
# api-gateway, bot-client, website). Everything here is either rebuilt inside
# the image (deps, dist), never used by any build stage (VCS, coverage,
# legacy), or must not leave the machine (.env*, local notes). voice-engine
# builds from its own context and is unaffected.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.astro
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
coverage
**/coverage
reports
junit.xml
**/junit.xml
tzurot-legacy
docs/local
.env
.env.*
